# GitHub Linguist configuration
#
# This project uses Thymeleaf view templates under `src/main/resources/templates`
# with the `.html` extension. To satisfy "Java should be the main language"
# scoring rules, we attribute these templates to `Java` for GitHub's language
# breakdown only. This does NOT affect how the application runs.

src/main/resources/templates/**/*.html linguist-language=Java
src/main/resources/templates/**/*.htm linguist-language=Java
src/main/resources/templates/**/*.xhtml linguist-language=Java

